We are happy to announce that our happy hours just gets hotter with Snow Crab included in the menu.
It’s only $11.99 per lb for: Shrimp, Clam, Mussel, Crawfish. For Snow Crab, it’s a half of a lb for only $11.99.
Monday to Friday: 03:00 PM - 07:00 PM. Saturday to Sunday: 12:00 PM - 05:00 PM
Ready for Christmas Party yet? Let us cook for you! We are accepting party trays order for Christmas Party and New Year. Please call us at (714) 829 4602 for more information.

Merry Christmas and Happy New Year to everyone! We are having these updates for Holiday Business Hours:
Christmas Eve: 09:00 AM - 03:00 PM. Christmas Day: 12:00 AM - 09:00 PM.
Let’s celebrate your Christmas with us all day long. We are having Happy Hours 12:00 PM - 05:00 PM.

Let’s celebrate MLK weekend at Clawszone. We also have happy hours on Saturday and Sunday (12:00 PM - 5:00 PM). $11.99 seafood per lb including Snow Crab (1/2 lb). Beers $4, Appetizers $10, and many more foods are waiting for you.
Happy Lunar New Year 2023. We would like to announce that we will be closed for Private Event on Saturday (01/21/2023) 1:00 PM - 6:00 PM. We will remain our regular hours after that. We will see you.

Dear our customers, we are closed tomorrow Monday (01/23/2023) for celebrating Lunar New Year 2023.
We will remain our regular business hour on Tuesday (01/24/2023). Thank you and Happy New Year.
Let’s stop by Clawszone Anaheim for amazing HAPPY HOURS. 🦀🦞🦐 Shrimp, Clam, Mussel, Crawfish are $11.99 per lb, Snow Crab is $11.99 per 1/2 lb. Beers are $4, and Appetizers are $10.
🦞🦞🦞Live crawfish is available in the house. We are having promotion BUY MORE PAY LESS🤑🤑🤑Please call us at ☎️(714) 829 4602 for more information.
FREE 1 LB Snow Crab or 1 Bottle of Wine when you spend minimum $60 on Valentine’s Weekend (02/11 - 02/14/2023) and Valentine’s Day. (This promotion is not combined with Happy Hours Menu)

TGIF! It’s even better to celebrate your weekend with our happy hour meal deals. Seafood is $11.99 per lb (Shrimp, Clam, Mussel, Crawfish) and Half Lb for Snow Crab. Beers are 50% OFF. And much more good food.

Live crawfish is in season now. They are jumbo in size, juicy in texture, and sweet in taste. Clawszone is having them in Happy Hours everyday. Please stop by our store to order them for dine in or takeout or you can call us at (714) 829 4602 for more information.
